        "testimonial_UPjm8b": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<h6><strong>Favorite Sandals </strong><br/>I have flat feet, bunions, plantar fasciitis, and have suffered from Achilles tendinitis. These sandals are wonderful! They look very attractive and fashionable while also providing the desperately needed support so that I can walk. I love the Velcro closures that can be adjusted across the toes, as well as around the ankle. I wish that I could get a pair in every color!”</h6>",
