          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<h6><strong>Very comfortable!</strong><br/>I have bunions and I need good arch support so I don’t skimp on shoes. These sandals were comfortable right out of the box. The adjustable straps make them a perfect fit and the arch support is great. <br/></h6><h6></h6>",
